  EffectDiscription_ENG: '[Main] Reveal the top 3 cards of your deck. Add 1 card
    with the [D-Brigade] or [DigiPolice] trait among them to the hand. Return the
    rest to the top of the deck. Then, place this card in the battle area.[Main]
    <Delay>Reveal the top 3 cards of your deck. You may play 1 card with the [D-Brigade]
    or [DigiPolice] trait and a play cost of 4 or less among them without paying
    the cost. Trash the rest.'
